    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This information is general guidance only. 
        Tax laws vary by jurisdiction. Please consult with a qualified tax professional 
        for advice specific to your situation.
      </p>
