  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Payment FAQ</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Common questions about getting paid</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">What happens if I don't reach the minimum threshold?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Your earnings roll over to the next payment period until you reach the minimum threshold. There's no expiration on accumulated earnings.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Can I change my payment method?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, you can update your payment method anytime in your dashboard settings. Changes take effect for the next payment cycle.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">What if there's an issue with my payment?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Contact our support team immediately. We'll investigate and re-process failed payments as quickly as possible, usually within 24 hours.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Are there any hidden fees?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">No hidden fees! All costs are clearly displayed in the comparison table above. Most payment methods are completely free.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>